Wild at Heart;;81;;68;;R;;After serving prison time for a self-defense killing, Sailor Ripley (Nicolas Cage) reunites with girlfriend Lula Fortune (Laura Dern). Lula's mother, Marietta (Diane Ladd), desperate to keep them apart, hires a hit man to kill Sailor. But he finds a whole new set of troubles when he and Bobby Peru (Willem Dafoe), an old buddy who's also out to get Sailor, try to rob a store. When Sailor lands in jail yet again, the young lovers appear further than ever from the shared life they covet.;;Drama;;David Lynch;;1990;;Nicolas Cage,Laura Dern,Diane Ladd,Willem Dafoe,Isabella Rossellini,Harry Dean Stanton,Crispin Glover,Grace Zabriskie,J.E. Freeman,William Morgan Sheppard;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wild_at_heart